Dialogue: 5,0:00:00.68,0:00:03.77,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she got angry at me after all.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:03.77,0:00:06.42,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,It was like she was possessed by a demon. {namahage?}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:06.42,0:00:11.21,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,I told her I'd run away from home, \Nand she said to go ahead and try it.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:11.21,0:00:14.03,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I tried to set her off and she called my bluff.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:14.03,0:00:14.61,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yadomi?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:14.87,0:00:16.72,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you bring this?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:16.72,0:00:18.64,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sleep without it.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:18.64,0:00:19.79,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,What about this towel?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:20.49,0:00:22.29,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,I need this to sleep too.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:22.68,0:00:25.23,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,You must be seriously sleep deprived.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:25.23,0:00:29.39,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down and think things through. You can't run away from home.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:29.39,0:00:32.00,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,And you shouldn't skip school either.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:32.00,0:00:33.80,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:34.32,0:00:35.77,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, Anjou.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:35.77,0:00:39.96,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've tried skipping school, it will get out of hand.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:41.01,0:00:42.85,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine at first.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:43.33,0:00:46.20,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing changes if you just skip one day.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:46.20,0:00:50.57,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}But since nothing changed, you tell yourself it's OK to skip one \Nmore day, and then another, and the days just keep adding up.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:50.57,0:00:52.94,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,And before you realize, you've already...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:52.94,0:00:57.05,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess I don't really have a right to lecture you about that.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:57.05,0:00:58.09,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:58.44,0:00:58.82,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:59.35,0:01:02.01,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You're right.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:02.01,0:01:05.04,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty amazing. You haven't lost \Nyour style while living as a shut-in.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:05.04,0:01:06.59,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Why bring that up...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:06.59,0:01:08.85,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,You really haven't changed.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:08.85,0:01:09.41,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:09.41,0:01:12.99,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you're going through, you only think of others.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:15.71,0:01:17.11,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out already!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:18.60,0:01:21.81,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,All you ever do is worry about others.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:23.10,0:01:25.06,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:25.65,0:01:27.02,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Menma's way more...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:29.24,0:01:31.00,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey listen...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:31.38,0:01:36.52,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,I talked to Yukiatsu, and he said that \Nwe're all still obsessed with Menma.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:36.52,0:01:39.56,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,And he said that maybe that's not healthy.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:39.56,0:01:42.19,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Say what you want, but she's at my house right now.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:42.73,0:01:44.75,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm talking about...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:44.75,0:01:48.24,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you don't believe in Menma?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:48.24,0:01:51.34,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not that I don't believe in her.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:53.05,0:01:55.49,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading home.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:56.40,0:01:57.80,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second, Yadomi.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:08.63,0:02:12.24,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,I bought some beef bowl curry.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:12.24,0:02:13.57,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 520 yen.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:19.66,0:02:20.95,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Beef bowl curry retreats!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.01,0:02:23.59,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:23.59,0:02:24.89,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I was just here for the diary...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,2.23 {?}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:26.33,0:02:28.95,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,My food{beef bowl curry}!{change this back if you want to}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,-OP-
Dialogue: 5,0:04:01.60,0:04:05.69,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,By reading this we might figure out Menma's wish.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:06.34,0:04:08.14,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.90,0:04:12.64,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,The Menma I don't know is in here.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:13.21,0:04:16.74,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,The things Menma thought that I don't know about are in here.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:31.02,0:04:32.15,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:32.15,0:04:33.18,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Halfheartedly done.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.18,0:04:36.95,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that's different is \Nwhether she says she had fun or a blast.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:37.26,0:04:40.46,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,She was bad at writing.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.46,0:04:42.75,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this one's a little different.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:42.75,0:04:46.97,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,I tripped while playing with everyone today. It hurt.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:46.97,0:04:49.02,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Look, this one's different too.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:49.02,0:04:53.23,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Today we all went to the hospital to visit Jintan's mom.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:53.92,0:04:55.95,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,We visited the hospital huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:56.84,0:05:01.35,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,We did do that often, all of us together.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:03.18,0:05:04.45,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:05.50,0:05:09.30,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan's mom is always in the hospital.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:09.72,0:05:12.71,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I have an idea! Let's all write a letter to God.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:12.98,0:05:16.66,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,"Please make Jintan's mom better soon!"
Dialogue: 5,0:05:16.66,0:05:17.84,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,How would we do that?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:21.53,0:05:23.28,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that Jintan!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:32.75,0:05:35.02,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I remember now. Back then...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:35.76,0:05:36.83,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.88,0:05:40.84,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,We decided that we'll make fireworks together.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.84,0:05:42.75,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,We think that it will be tough.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:42.75,0:05:45.06,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,But we'll do our best.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:46.04,0:05:47.50,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Now I remember!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:47.50,0:05:51.36,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,We were going to attach a letter to a rocket and send it to God.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:51.36,0:05:54.20,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think this is her wish?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.20,0:05:56.68,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! That must be it.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:56.68,0:05:59.34,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,We wanted to make one but in the end we couldn't.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:59.34,0:06:00.49,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think Yadomi?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:03.24,0:06:05.09,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,For my mom...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:11.84,0:06:13.35,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Late Jintan.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:13.91,0:06:15.47,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Delinquent Jintan.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:16.09,0:06:17.39,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Evil Jintan.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.84,0:06:21.87,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Ouchie.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:35.25,0:06:37.94,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't thinking about Jintan at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.15,0:06:49.64,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,You'll turn into a pig if you eat late at night.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.64,0:06:51.39,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who'll turn into a pig.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.58,0:06:59.06,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,That's salt ramen. With egg.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:59.48,0:07:01.51,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,They were out of Ken-chan ramen.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:02.20,0:07:05.14,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd cheer you up by giving you a treat.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:06.09,0:07:07.35,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:11.07,0:07:13.52,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,It's tasty!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:13.52,0:07:16.94,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,My dad's coming home soon, so hurry up.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:18.78,0:07:21.79,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I'm going to school tomorrow too.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:22.76,0:07:25.60,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,So... don't follow me.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:32.39,0:07:33.30,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm proud of you!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:35.67,0:07:37.25,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Here's you reward.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.95,0:07:39.78,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want it.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:41.12,0:07:43.94,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Just make sure not to do weird stuff anymore. {I think she means leaving the house at night}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:47.78,0:07:51.71,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,So why are you wearing your uniform \Neven though you're skipping school?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:51.71,0:07:55.07,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem? I have the freedom \Nto choose the way I dress and...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:55.07,0:07:55.84,Default,Yukiatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:55.84,0:07:56.61,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:57.78,0:08:01.59,Default,Yukiatsu,0000,0000,0000,,According to the Conflagrating Substance Control Law,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:01.59,0:08:05.09,Default,Yukiatsu,0000,0000,0000,,You have to be 18 to get a nationally recognized \Nlicense to possess or handle fireworks.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:05.17,0:08:06.58,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:06.58,0:08:09.67,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like little toy fireworks are an exception,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:10.20,0:08:11.88,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,but you need a license for those too.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:13.75,0:08:15.29,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's hopeless.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:15.29,0:08:19.79,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. If you think about it, we're not even \Nremotely qualified to make fireworks...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:19.79,0:08:22.94,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, while cleaning the other day...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:25.54,0:08:26.90,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Is this for real?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:27.52,0:08:32.03,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Get a bunch of fireworks and mix the \Npowder together to make one big one!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:32.76,0:08:34.80,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Stick it into a toilet paper roll.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:34.80,0:08:36.04,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,No! It'll burn!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:36.04,0:08:37.03,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the point?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:37.42,0:08:38.87,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,This is scary! Kids are scary!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:39.80,0:08:44.60,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,But back then we thought this could work.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.50,0:08:50.80,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We really thought we could get this flying back then.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:52.75,0:08:55.14,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,It would be way cooler than anything we had seen at festivals.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:55.65,0:08:57.74,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,We thought we could get it to fly.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:05.20,0:09:06.57,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,It flew!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:07.03,0:09:13.11,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}High-schoolers looked like old people to us back then, but \Nwe thought we'd be able to do anything once we got there.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:20.28,0:09:25.54,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Now it feels like we were more free to do anything back then.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:27.97,0:09:32.32,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,We agreed to think about how to proceed,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:32.67,0:09:37.05,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,but really, it's hopeless no matter how you look at it.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:37.05,0:09:38.17,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.17,0:09:40.19,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep one thing in mind.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:40.19,0:09:44.93,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,If this isn't Menma's wish that you keep talking \Nabout, it'll just be a wild goose chase.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:45.88,0:09:50.67,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Have you confirmed it with the Menma who's at your house?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:50.67,0:09:51.52,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiatsu.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.46,0:09:56.59,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Asking her...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:57.56,0:10:00.60,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Asking her directly is kind of scary.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:03.61,0:10:04.49,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:06.27,0:10:07.77,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Déjà vu.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:07.77,0:10:08.37,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:08.64,0:10:13.73,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,There's Jintan, always forging ahead. \NAnd poor Yukiatsu, seeing him off.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:15.90,0:10:18.46,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,So why didn't you tell everyone?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:19.05,0:10:24.47,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,If he hadn't told us to meet up at the hideout that day...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:24.47,0:10:28.13,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Menma call us out that day?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:28.13,0:10:28.85,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:30.00,0:10:33.36,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She called me by phone.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.88,0:10:35.22,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,By phone?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:36.57,0:10:40.32,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. She said she had something to talk about.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:40.70,0:10:43.42,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,You've finally remembered that, so why didn't you tell everyone?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:44.16,0:10:45.62,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Because Yadomi was there.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:45.62,0:10:46.40,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:46.40,0:10:48.46,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're forgetting something important.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:50.46,0:10:55.15,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Menma told us to keep the meeting a secret from Yadomi.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:58.17,0:10:59.46,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Menma said that?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:01.76,0:11:02.69,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:03.33,0:11:05.16,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I know someone who make them.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:05.16,0:11:06.19,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:06.19,0:11:11.86,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. An old guy from my work says he \Nworks as a pyrotechnician during festivals.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:11.86,0:11:14.04,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to make fireworks?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:14.04,0:11:16.38,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,What? Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:16.38,0:11:17.35,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:18.15,0:11:21.74,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Why? No reason really.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:21.74,0:11:22.81,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,By yourself?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:22.81,0:11:26.06,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. With Popo and the others.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:29.09,0:11:30.57,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:30.57,0:11:32.50,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:32.50,0:11:35.31,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it is. I'll ask him for you then.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:36.33,0:11:39.68,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan Jintan JINTAN JINTAN!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:39.68,0:11:42.64,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get out of Condal City!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:40.13,0:11:42.64,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you think? I'll get in touch with him.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:42.64,0:11:44.90,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk about that later.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:44.90,0:11:45.99,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:47.75,0:11:52.29,Default,Dude,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, even the simple ones will cost you around that much.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:52.29,0:11:54.90,Default,Dude,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I'm not willing to let you try to make one though.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.16,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:03.16,0:12:04.31,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:08.16,0:12:09.27,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,200,000 yen?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:09.56,0:12:13.30,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, I haven't ever seen that much cash.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:13.30,0:12:14.57,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I know right.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:15.37,0:12:18.09,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It'll work out somehow.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:18.52,0:12:21.22,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Anaru and I can work ourselves to death with part-time jobs, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:21.22,0:12:24.45,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,How about you stop deciding things for me?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:24.45,0:12:25.60,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Part-time work.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.60,0:12:27.79,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a good idea? We'd be helping each other out.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:27.79,0:12:28.77,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:28.77,0:12:31.53,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,What? It'll be easy if you work seven days a week!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:31.53,0:12:34.01,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? I still haven't agreed to do it.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:34.01,0:12:35.08,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it too.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:35.08,0:12:37.52,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work part-time too.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:40.32,0:12:42.65,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,You enter the cash you receive here.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:43.01,0:12:45.54,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,This is the used price, and this one's for new items...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:45.54,0:12:48.31,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and so you put the balance in here.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:50.06,0:12:53.51,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,How come you've instantly picked up the \Ntechnique it took me a month to master...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:53.51,0:12:56.17,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,It took you way too long.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:58.20,0:12:59.56,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:59.56,0:13:00.71,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:02.97,0:13:05.30,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,You suck at this part.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:05.30,0:13:06.55,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:07.08,0:13:08.30,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the next group.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:08.30,0:13:09.18,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:10.18,0:13:12.52,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She's that girl people are talking about.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:12.79,0:13:14.54,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So she showed up to her job.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:14.54,0:13:16.58,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,She skipped school but...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:16.58,0:13:19.33,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Hey is that the guy who doesn't go to school?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:19.33,0:13:21.41,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. You think they're hookin' up?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:21.41,0:13:23.13,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,That must be nice. I want to hit that too...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:23.13,0:13:27.47,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,W-el-come!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:27.96,0:13:29.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with him?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:32.19,0:13:33.48,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,H-how was that?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:35.16,0:13:36.46,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that awesome?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:39.15,0:13:40.92,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:43.83,0:13:44.92,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:47.85,0:13:49.70,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,When we're like this...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:51.12,0:13:52.90,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same way it was back then.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:54.62,0:13:56.23,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hand me the tape Jintan.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:02.46,0:14:04.65,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ya...domi. {Ya, dominate me}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:06.99,0:14:08.57,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Catch, Anaru.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:09.57,0:14:11.16,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Pretend that didn't happen!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:11.16,0:14:12.42,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Nice catch.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:18.64,0:14:20.75,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yadomi's got a job?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:20.75,0:14:23.05,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like he's serious about the fireworks.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:25.25,0:14:28.96,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do? Should we set up some kind of fund-raiser?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.96,0:14:31.22,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to get caught up in Yadomi's little hobbies?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:31.70,0:14:34.01,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass if you're not going to participate.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:35.04,0:14:37.18,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wanna hang out a bit?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.98,0:14:40.51,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,We could grab tea or something.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:42.45,0:14:44.43,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't. I have exams coming up.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:44.43,0:14:46.24,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're not ranked fourth in your year for nothing.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:46.24,0:14:48.85,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,The guy ranked second in his year shouldn't be talking.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:48.85,0:14:49.80,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:53.75,0:14:57.45,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Hanging out with you brings its own difficulties you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:02.45,0:15:03.50,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Back to work.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:04.04,0:15:05.59,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:08.26,0:15:11.30,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,You're so late, Jintan... you delinquent!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:13.41,0:15:14.69,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:14.69,0:15:16.46,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take a bath.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:17.59,0:15:20.05,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely acting weird.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:23.40,0:15:25.48,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,He goes to sleep right away at night.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.10,0:15:26.90,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:27.45,0:15:29.09,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:27.87,0:15:30.19,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,He leaves right away in the morning.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:30.19,0:15:32.24,Default,TV,0000,0000,0000,,Time for today's Puppy Corner.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:32.58,0:15:36.63,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,If the puppy is a girl, it means \NJintan is doing something weird. {she's not saying Jintan would fuck a dog; it's like she's flipping a coin to decide if Jintan is doing something weird}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:34.95,0:15:37.20,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this pumpkin is perfect!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:37.20,0:15:41.10,Default,TV,0000,0000,0000,,Today's puppy is Oscar, a girl. She's 7 years old.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:41.68,0:15:42.95,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Pugs are cute.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:42.95,0:15:44.15,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Wrinkles are cute.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:44.15,0:15:45.15,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,It's a girl.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:46.00,0:15:48.88,Default,TV,0000,0000,0000,,...say greetings, like "Welcome!"
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.42,0:15:48.88,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Coming.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:51.59,0:15:52.77,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:52.77,0:15:54.04,Default,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:54.04,0:15:55.70,Default,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,If you could sign here...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.70,0:15:57.69,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. Let's see...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:57.69,0:16:00.94,Default,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, did Jinta quit school?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:00.94,0:16:04.81,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,No. But why do you ask?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:04.81,0:16:07.10,Default,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for bringing it up.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:07.73,0:16:12.28,Default,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,But a little while ago I saw him... \NI guess he was working a part-time job?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:13.06,0:16:17.71,Default,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Has he told you about that?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:17.71,0:16:22.41,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes. But you could say I'm a proponent of free will.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:22.41,0:16:26.43,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I let Jintan decide on his own. It's fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.61,0:16:29.49,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,No it's not! It's not fine! It's not fine!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:29.49,0:16:30.08,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fine!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:30.60,0:16:33.05,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fine!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:39.36,0:16:40.41,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Anaru.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:44.21,0:16:45.37,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Poppo.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:45.37,0:16:50.21,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm not scheduled today, but \Napparently the manager took a liking to him.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:51.28,0:16:53.49,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're working with him tonight though, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:54.22,0:16:56.74,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,What? The Hitsujiyama construction site?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:56.74,0:16:58.76,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that going a little overboard?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:58.76,0:17:03.72,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right. Skilled labor pays the best.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:04.27,0:17:07.79,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rocket fireworks are fueled by money.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:10.00,0:17:11.40,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:13.43,0:17:14.84,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:15.85,0:17:17.15,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,...wish.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:18.51,0:17:20.95,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Think about yourself a little more!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:21.47,0:17:24.04,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Your attitude pisses me off!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:29.29,0:17:32.25,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:33.20,0:17:36.34,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, did Yukiatsu get in touch with you?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:36.34,0:17:38.45,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah you know, we talk every once in a while.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:38.45,0:17:40.74,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,It would be nice if they came by too.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.96,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious they're worried about Jintan.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:42.96,0:17:44.31,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Jintan?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:45.73,0:17:48.34,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,What? Jintan's Jintan. That's what you call him.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:48.34,0:17:51.63,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with me calling him Jintan?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:52.16,0:17:53.27,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.00,0:17:57.53,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:03.24,0:18:04.79,Default,Dude,0000,0000,0000,,Over here, new guy!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:05.85,0:18:06.98,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:10.25,0:18:11.85,Default,Dude,0000,0000,0000,,Come over here next.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:11.85,0:18:12.59,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:13.70,0:18:15.72,Default,Dude,0000,0000,0000,,He's giving it his all.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:17.45,0:18:20.79,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. He's really cool.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:20.79,0:18:22.17,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:29.43,0:18:34.15,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,While I haven't been thinking about myself...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:34.15,0:18:40.20,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan has always been thinking about me.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:41.76,0:18:44.63,Default,Dude,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, watch your step.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:44.63,0:18:45.79,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:01.70,0:19:05.79,Default,Dude,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? Don't change the angle of the light on your own!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:05.79,0:19:06.65,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:06.65,0:19:08.96,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the wind?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:08.96,0:19:11.92,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You think the wind could move that light?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:16.49,0:19:21.15,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cool. You're glowing, Jintan.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:27.15,0:19:28.86,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,You're cool.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:36.35,0:19:37.60,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,All this?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:38.05,0:19:40.19,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I made plenty!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:40.19,0:19:41.80,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,You need to learn some moderation.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:50.06,0:19:50.97,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,It's tasty!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:50.97,0:19:51.71,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:52.52,0:19:55.63,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,It tastes a lot like the ones my mom made.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:59.04,0:20:02.01,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,So Jintan, is school tough?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:02.01,0:20:05.95,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but it's also fun.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:05.95,0:20:07.04,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:07.04,0:20:09.06,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, how can I put it...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:09.40,0:20:12.86,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it unexpectedly feels better than always staying at home.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:12.86,0:20:15.48,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I feel alive while I'm there.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:16.67,0:20:17.86,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Alive...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:17.86,0:20:21.70,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I didn't mean that literally...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:21.70,0:20:24.62,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, up until now I've been...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:24.62,0:20:32.75,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Me too. I also feel alive when I look at you while you feel alive!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:32.75,0:20:34.11,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Menma.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:38.99,0:20:41.13,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought a deposit.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:43.59,0:20:48.83,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's not nearly enough, but could I get started on it now?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:48.83,0:20:49.88,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:51.21,0:20:55.61,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, about that. I'm sorry, but I can't help you out.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:56.50,0:20:59.68,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I accidentally let it slip to the director of the festival...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:59.68,0:21:03.57,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I got scolded for offering to teach high-schoolers this stuff.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:03.57,0:21:05.35,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:05.35,0:21:06.39,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:06.39,0:21:08.03,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,We worked so hard!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:08.65,0:21:10.59,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this festival director?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:10.59,0:21:12.04,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk directly to them!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:12.50,0:21:15.25,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's one of the Honmas.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:18.91,0:21:20.40,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Someone from Menma's family?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:25.84,0:21:32.90,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Jinta and the \Nothers are trying their best for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:38.53,0:21:40.22,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,They're all messing around. {could be insulting, 'they're screwing around,' but I'm not sure since adults can use the phrase to describe playing children - 'they're full of energy'; reading Japanese twitter comments, I think the insulting version fits best}{i can't see her mom saying "screwing around"}
