Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.51,0:22:19.47,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forget the hopes and dreams \Nwe shared during that one summer's end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.64,0:22:26.56,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we will meet again in another \NAugust, in maybe ten years time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.73,0:22:33.78,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I could feel your heartfelt thanks all the way until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.90,0:22:36.57,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,And I know it must've been painful
